lead_paragraph: Out-of-form Australia batsman Nic Maddinson has been granted a reprieve with his captain Steve Smith confirming his side would be unchanged for the Boxing Day test against Pakistan.

headline.print_headline: Maddinson Survives as Australia Unchanged for Boxing Day Test
